@startuml ZMQ RPC Metrics — Current Code (2026-05 snapshot)
' Companion to timing_points.puml: that file保留历史叙事；本图对齐 yuanrong-datasystem 当前实现。
!pragma teoz true
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actorBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title **ZMQ RPC ticks & histograms — lifecycle (aligned with current sources)**

participant "Caller" as C <<Client>>
box "Stub (templates in zmq_stub_impl.h)" #LightBlue
participant "AsyncWriteImpl" as AW
participant "AsyncReadImpl" as AR
end box
participant "MsgQueRef /\noutbound" as R <<Queue>>
participant "MsgQueMgr prefetch\n→ Outbound()" as OB <<Route>>
participant "ZmqFrontend::SendMsg\n(zmq_stub_conn.cpp)" as FE <<Frontend>>
participant "Frontend msgQue_\n(+ async send thread)" as AS <<AsyncGW>>
database "TCP / IPC" as Net
participant "ZmqService /\nRecv path" as SRV <<Server>>
participant "WorkerEntry\n(zmq_service.cpp)" as W <<Worker>>
participant "Unary Write()\n(enableMsgQ_)\nzmq_server_stream_base.h" as UW <<Reply>>
participant "ZmqService::\nServiceToClient" as STC <<Backend>>
participant "ZmqServerImpl::\nServiceToClient" as IMPL <<GW>>

note top
**Ticks** (MetaPb.tick_name — current sources)

* **CLIENT_ENQUEUE** → **zmq_stub_impl.h** AsyncWriteImpl, before outer **mQue->SendMsg**

* **CLIENT_TO_STUB** → **zmq_stub_conn.cpp**, start of **ZmqStubConnMgrImpl::Outbound**
  (after **MsgQueMgr::PrefetchMsg** dequeues from per-stub outbound; still **before** frontend inner queue /
  ``zmq_msg_send``)

* (none on request wire-out) → **CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND** still missing (prefetcher vs **clientMeta**)

* **CLIENT_RECV** → **zmq_stub_impl.h** AsyncReadImpl after **ReceiveMsg**

* **SERVER_RECV** / **SERVER_DEQUEUE** → recv path + **WorkerEntry** after **ReceiveMsg**

* **SERVER_EXEC_END** → may repeat (**Unary Write()** plus **WorkerEntry** tail — duplicate risk)

* **SERVER_SEND** → **Write()** /**ServiceToClient** — **ZmqServerImpl::ServiceToClient** has **no**
  ``TICK_SERVER_ZMQ_SEND`` after **SendAllFrames**

* **SERVER_EXEC_NS** → synthetic (**RecordServerLatencyMetrics**), EXEC_END − RECV (**zmq_constants.h**)


**Histograms** (same headers)

* ``zmq_client_queuing`` → ``TO_STUB − ENQUEUE`` (caller enqueue through prefetch dequeue, before frontend zmq stack)

* server: DEQUEUE−RECV, EXEC_END−DEQUEUE, SEND−EXEC_END

* ``zmq_rpc_e2e`` = RECV − ENQUEUE; ``zmq_rpc_network`` ≈ e2e − (TO_STUB−ENQUEUE) − ``SERVER_RPC_WINDOW_NS`` (**not** pure RTT)

end note

== Request (client) ==

C -> AW : AsyncWriteImpl
activate AW
AW -> AW : RecordTick: **CLIENT_ENQUEUE**
AW -> R : mQue->SendMsg(meta, frames)
activate R
R -> R : MsgQue outbound **enqueue**
R -> OB : prefetcher ``PrefetchMsg`` → ``routeFn`` → **Outbound(sender, meta+frames)**
activate OB
OB -> OB : RecordTick: **CLIENT_TO_STUB**
OB -> FE : **SendMsg**(→ inner queue / async gateway)
activate FE
FE -> AS : msgQue_->Send(ConnMsgFrames); later RouteToZmqSocket → ``zmq_msg_send``
deactivate FE
deactivate OB
deactivate R
note over AS
  **无 MetaPb tick** 于真正 ``zmq_msg_send`` 完成处
end note
deactivate AW

AS -> Net : request bytes
Net -> SRV : delivery
activate SRV
SRV -> SRV : RecordTick: **SERVER_RECV**
SRV -> W : dispatch → WorkerEntry
activate W
W -> W : ReceiveMsg → RecordTick **SERVER_DEQUEUE**
W -> UW : impl_->CallMethod → … Write(reply)
activate UW
UW -> UW : RecordTick **SERVER_EXEC_END**, **SERVER_SEND**\nRecordServerLatencyMetrics(meta)\n(追加 **SERVER_EXEC_NS**  synthetic)
UW -> STC : mQue_->SendMsg / reply path
deactivate UW

STC -> STC : RecordTick **SERVER_SEND**\nRecordServerLatencyMetrics (again if hit)
STC -> IMPL : replyQueue → ServiceToClient
activate IMPL
IMPL -> IMPL : PushFront… + **frontend_->SendAllFrames**\n(此处 **无** RecordTick TICK_SERVER_ZMQ_SEND)
IMPL -> Net : response bytes
deactivate IMPL
deactivate W
deactivate SRV

Net -> AR : reply
activate AR
C -> AR : AsyncReadImpl → ReceiveMsg
AR -> AR : RecordTick **CLIENT_RECV**
AR -> AR : merge clientMeta.ticks → rsp.first
AR -> AR : **RecordRpcLatencyMetrics**(rsp.first)

deactivate AR

== Notes for PR / docs ==
note across
  **与 timing_points.puml 的差异**
  • 已不再使用字面 **CLIENT_DEQUEUE**；**CLIENT_TO_STUB** 语义对齐 **Prefetcher 出队后**（**Outbound** 首行），而非 **ZmqFrontend::SendMsg** 入口。
  • 回包侧重命名 **SERVER_SEND**，**不是**只在 zmq_server_impl.cpp 打完 zmq_send 后打 **SERVER_ZMQ_SEND**（常量存在与否与 unary 路径需再统一）。
  • **Unary + enableMsgQ_**：**SERVER_EXEC_END** 可能在 Write 与 WorkerEntry 末尾各打一次 → 度量若取「最后一个同名 tick」会吞掉异步 SendAll 时间，PR 793 建议在代码或文档固定语义。

  **PerfPoint（非 histogram）**：ParseMsgFrames 里 **GetLapTime** 打点 **ZMQ_NETWORK_TRANSFER (SERVER)** 可作传输辅助，但与 **zmq_rpc_network_latency** 公式不同。
end note

@enduml
